text: Michelena TV is a Venezuelan community television channel. It was created in December 2002 and can be seen in the community of Michelena in the Michelena Municipality of the Tachira State of Venezuela on UHF channel 39. Luis Enrique Jaimes is the legal representative of the foundation that owns this channel.
